es: <br><br>Griffen Feather-most any griffens near Karanas or vendors in Rathe, NK, and probably Jaggedpine. <br>Cyclops Toes-SeaFuries in OOT (level 39-42) and Cyclops in SK, RM, WK (level 28 - 42) or Gornit in OOT. <br>Broom-Magicians (level 9-24) in Najena and Alligators (level 18-34) in Feerrott.<br>Star Ruby-from vendor.<br>------------------------------------------------<br>Stien of Ulissa (increases size and power of a summoned Water Elementals above level 34) requires:<br><br>Mermaid scale-Sirens on the spires in OOT<br>Ice Giant Toes-Ice Giants in Everfrost Peaks or from Gornit. <br>Stien-Magicians in Najena and Alligators in Feerrott, Magicians (level 9 -24) and Alligators (level 18-34). <br>Sapphire-from vendor. <br><br>[these notes were gathered from my experience and other posts, thank you for your help you know who you are]</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><span style='color: Maroon;'>Lineage2 <a href=HTTP://www.angelfire.com/cantina/advyl/BobVilla/crafting.html target=akztarg>crafting guide</a>.<br>EQ website <a href=HTTP://www.angelfire.com/cantina/advyl/index.html target=akztarg>Advyl's Helping Hand</a>.</td></tr>
